quran[8{c,v,t}:
7,23,"dono bol utthay,"" ae rab, hum ne apne oopar sitam kya, ab agar to ne hum se Dur guzar nah farmaya aur reham nah kya to yaqeenan hum tabah ho jayen ge """
7,24,"farmaya,"" utar jao, tum aik dosray ke dushman ho, aur tumahray liye aik khaas muddat taq zameen hi mein jaye qarar aur samaan zeist hai """
7,25,"aur farmaya,"" wahein tum ko jeena aur wahein marna hai aur isi mein se tum ko aakhir kaar nikala jaye ga """
7,26,"ae aulaad aadam, hum ne tum par libaas nazil kya hai ke tumahray jism ke qabil sharam hisson ko dhanke aur tumahray liye jism ki hifazat aur zeenat ka zareya bhi ho, aur behtareen libaas taqwa ka libaas hai yeh Allah ki nshanyon mein se aik nishani hai, shayad ke log is se sabaq len"
7,27,"ae bani aadam, aisa nah ho ke shetan tumhe phir usi terhan ftne mein mubtala kar day jis terhan is ne tumahray walidain ko jannat se nklwaya tha aur a noon ke libaas un par se utarwa diye thay taakay un kisharmghain aik dosray ke samnay khole woh aur is ke saathi tumhe aisi jagah se dekhte hain jahan se tum inhen nahi dekh satke inn shyatin ko hum ne unn logon ka sarparast bana diya hai jo imaan nahi laatay"
7,28,yeh log jab koi sharamnaak kaam karte hain to kehte hain hum ne apne baap dada ko isi tareeqa par paaya hai aur Allah hi ne hamein aisa karne ka hukum diya hai inn se kaho Allah be hiyai ka hukum kabhi nahi diya karta kya tum Allah ka naam le kar woh baatein kehte ho jin ke mutaliq tumhe ilm nahi hai ( woh Allah ki taraf se hain ) ?
7,29,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho, mere rab ne to raasti o insaaf ka hukum diya hai, aur is ka hukum to yeh hai ke har ibadat mein apna rukh theek rakho aur usi ko poukaro apne deen ko is ke liye khalis rakh kar jis terhan uss ne tumhe ab peda kya hai isi terhan tum phir peda kiye jao ge"
7,30,"aik giroh koto is ne seedha rasta dikha diya hai, magar dosray giroh par gumraahi chaspan ho kar reh gayi hai, kyunkay unhon ne khuda ke bajaye shyatin ko apna sir parast bana liya hai aur woh samajh rahay hain ke hum seedhi raah par hain"
